  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dda \u0db4\u0dde\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A private bus strike in Akuressa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thousands of passengers were stranded at the main bus station after starting a private bus strike in Akuresse.",
        "The private bus workers say that they started this strike because diesel was not released from Akurassa depot yesterday. The strike will continue until diesel is received.",
        "However, although only a few Langama buses were running, it seemed that they were not enough for the needs of the passengers.",
        "Attempts were made to contact Mr. Bimal Danushka, Manager of Akurassa Langama Depot, by phone to inquire about this, but failed."
      ],
